[center][size=5][/size][/center][center][color=#ff7700][size=5]FREE Palette For enb[/size]

[color=#ffffff]The palette must be named "enbpalette" and be in BMP format.[/color]

Never ever be used in a paid mod.
Not all palettes are shown as a example, simply because my Skyrim did not take the screenshot.
Will add the examples later, and will add more palettes to use.

[color=#e06666]This may not be everyone´s cup of tea, but with some tweaking I'm sure great things can be made.
I will not tolerate rude language or insults. [/color]

[/color][/center]
